# Real environment files with secrets — never commit these.
# The committed templates are the various `.env.example` files.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# Exception: committed NON-SECRET, project-specific Functions runtime config
# (loaded by `firebase deploy`). Secrets never live here — use Secret Manager.
!functions/.env.childbook-60f89

